36
00:04:35,191 --> 00:04:36,067
Misalnya…

37
00:04:36,776 --> 00:04:38,653
-Karena kamu sudah menikah?
-TIDAK.

38
00:04:39,487 --> 00:04:40,655
Bukan itu sebabnya…

39
00:04:41,698 --> 00:04:42,949
Saya belum menikah.

40
